title: Baba Kalyani
subTitle: Baba Kalyani, a police officer, travels to Kochi to uncover a terrorist conspiracy. He must not only work on the case but also deal with old rivals who are hell-bent on settling scores with him.

title: Again Kasargod Khader Bhai
subTitle: Kasim Bhai is found murdered. The suspicion falls on the Kaladarshana team and the unfolding of the murder mystery forms the rest of the story.

title: Cheriya Kallanum Valiya Poleesum
subTitle: Sadasivan comes across a house where the owner, Kumaran, has committed suicide to protect his wife, Soumini. However, what is even stranger is that a man who is visually challenged is always around.

title: Pachuvum Kovalanum
subTitle: For TV director Thomaskutty Pachu, nothing is more stressful than dealing with his pesky cousin Joseph Kovalan. That is, until a murder occurs on the set.

title: Chirikkum Thalika
subTitle: A comprehensive compilation of some of the best rib-tickling comedy scenes from various Malayalam movies featuring renowned actors and actresses.

title: Ohm Shanthi Oshaana
subTitle: Pooja Mathew, a spirited young girl, dreams about marrying only for love. Thus, she stops at nothing to impress Giri, who saved her once from a group of unruly men.

title: Evidam Swargamanu
subTitle: Mathews owns a farm that is the envy of everyone in the village. It attracts the attention of a dirty land dealer, who entangles him in a vicious bureaucratic web to take it away from him.

title: Ring Master
subTitle: Prince, a dog trainer, faces an awkward situation when his pet dog Diana acts in a film alongside his former lover, an actress who shares the same name as the dog.

title: Oru Marubhoomikkadha
subTitle: Madhavan is an honest and hardworking man. However, when a rich man's daughter, Eliana, asks him to abduct her and demand a ransom from her father, his life turns upside down.

title: Guruvayur Ambalanadayil
subTitle: A young man eagerly awaits his wedding, but fate twists cruelly, forcing him into a lifelong bond with a woman who harbours nothing but resentment for him.

title: Lucifer
subTitle: The demise of the leader of a political party leads to a massive power struggle. Amidst the chaos, a mystical man named Stephen comes in to ascend the throne.

title: Lucifer
subTitle: The demise of the leader of a political party leads to a massive power struggle. Amidst the chaos, a mystical man named Stephen comes in to ascend the throne.

title: Niram
subTitle: Aby realises that he is in love with Sona, his childhood friend, but is unable to express his feelings. However, he faces a dilemma when he learns that her marriage has already been arranged.

title: Irul
subTitle: Alex and Archana go on a trip but soon their car breaks down, and they take shelter at a nearby house. However, things take a turn when the owner of the house behaves in a suspicious manner.

title: Killadi Raman
subTitle: Mahadevan is a live witness of Radhika's hit-and-run accident. His helpful gesture of taking Radhika to the hospital, however, lands him in trouble when he is confronted by Meera, Radhika's friend.

title: Chirikkum Thalika
subTitle: A comprehensive compilation of some of the best rib-tickling comedy scenes from various Malayalam movies featuring renowned actors and actresses.

title: Love Action Drama
subTitle: Dinesh, a conceited and wealthy young bachelor, goes to extreme lengths to impress a girl named Shobha with the help of his best friend Sagar, and Dinesh eventually hopes to marry Shobha.

title: Udayananu Tharam
subTitle: A struggling director gets cheated by his friend who steals his script and becomes a famous actor. However, when he finally gets the chance to direct a film, he is forced to cast a dubious actor.

title: Pulimurugan
subTitle: A small village seeks help from a man with extraordinary force to protect them against man-eating tigers and the drug mafia.

title: Lucky Baskhar
subTitle: Desperate to bring his family out of monetary woes, Baskhar Kumar, a bank employee, enters the dangerous and murky world of financial scams.

title: Bramayugam
subTitle: A folk singer in 17th-century Kerala flees slavery and discovers a mansion. Inside, he encounters an enigmatic cook and a powerful master, setting in motion a chain of events that changes his life.

title: Johny Johny Yes Appa
subTitle: Johny pretends to be a gentleman but is a thief who thrives on lies and betrayals. His life turns upside down after his encounter with Adam, an orphan.

title: Johny Johny Yes Appa
subTitle: Johny pretends to be a gentleman but is a thief who thrives on lies and betrayals. His life turns upside down after his encounter with Adam, an orphan.

title: Thaskara Lahala
subTitle: Three inseparable friends devise an ingenious ploy to fund a destitute woman's marriage. However, destiny plays a cruel game after an unscrupulous individual steal their hard-earned funds.

title: Parayam
subTitle: Raju's father is desperate to help his son find true love. However, trouble ensues when Raju develops feelings for Sudha, who harbours affection for someone else.

title: Maniyarakallan
subTitle: Kasthuri moves to a different city to escape from a man, who has an eye on her will. However, her life is in danger when he sends his thugs in search of her.

title: Robinhood
subTitle: A thief robs the automated teller machines of the Imperial Bank of India. Worried about the safety of the bank, the managing director decides to hire a private detective to solve the case.

title: Kilichundan Mambazham
subTitle: Moidukutty Haji returns to his village after taking a third wife, despite his other wives' disapproval. Unbeknownst to him, his young and beautiful new bride, Amina, is secretly in love with Abdu, a bangle seller.

title: Karyasthan
subTitle: After a past incident, two powerful clans of Krishnapuram remain estranged until one day, a man with a mysterious past decides to bring the families together.

title: Adi Kapyare Koottamani
subTitle: Lakshmi, hoping to enter and exit the college hostel unnoticed, offers Bhanuprasad, a student, a sum of money. However, she ends up trapped in the building due to a series of chaotic events.

title: Ponman
subTitle: Ajesh, a gold dealer, lends some gold jewelry for a village wedding, unaware of the betrayal ahead. However, the bride's husband plans to keep the gold and kill Ajesh.

title: Ittymaani: Made in China
subTitle: Ittymaani, who was raised in China, runs a business of counterfeit products in India. However, when he tries to help Annamma who is ignored by her sons, he lands in trouble because she falls ill.
